Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,== OCR ==
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.07,0:01:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.64,0:01:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,積蒙塔…逐漸變成格拉迪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.84,0:01:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能留在這裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.81,0:01:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,積蒙塔…變成格拉迪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡  怎麼也贏不了她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絲莉亞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.26,0:03:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她一直那樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:43.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米奇…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.23,0:03:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會記起的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.67,0:03:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為米奇那麼似人類
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:50.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他心底某處  他一定記得你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.34,0:03:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  蓮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.14,0:03:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在  我們已經絕望嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不會絕望的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那裡的工具箱拿給我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉謝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.30,0:04:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會否駕駛  我不管
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在能做的只有這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去絲莉亞身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絲莉亞現在需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.23,0:04:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  這樣又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.36,0:04:50.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了  我為何這麼聰明的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格拉迪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.58,0:05:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,NSA間諜衛星的映像
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.88,0:05:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看  格拉迪亞正飛向傘子的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傘子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:15.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,素成計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個世上已經無人去進行那計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:22.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格拉迪亞打算接手進行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:23.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但目的卻不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.87,0:05:30.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,素成計劃是把大氣層外的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,純淨太陽光聚集在傘子上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.61,0:05:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後以光線形態送進積蒙塔內
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.01,0:05:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼而儲存在地底的龍脈裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:40.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新聞有報導過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:44.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一向對那種事都不感興趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.05,0:05:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東京的龍脈正在亞人化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.96,0:05:49.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.19,0:05:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我們把龍脈封鎖在東京都內
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果更強大的費挪現象出現…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她打算從宇宙散播費挪現象嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是最有效率的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.20,0:06:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對什麼有效率
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把地球的機械全部變成亞人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.45,0:06:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說過這是NSA的衛星映像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.78,0:06:15.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,NSA發射了飛彈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然在這種地方使用核彈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.99,0:06:23.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,核彈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飛彈給亞人化了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有國家都一片混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.66,0:07:04.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們全都害怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的國家會變成跟東京一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:08.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  若給他們知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.97,0:07:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格拉迪亞控制了素成計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.61,0:07:13.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那便麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.11,0:07:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.48,0:07:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把光線的接收器毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向東京投擲核彈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.72,0:07:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去追格迪拉亞  然後消滅她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.19,0:07:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都想快點離開這種城市
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只是覺得有趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得痛快…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.07,0:07:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才一直消滅失常亞人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去賺取零用錢罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們根本不想遇上悲傷的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.65,0:07:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人生不如意事十常八九
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.55,0:08:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像自己心愛的女人另有心上人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.72,0:08:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我不會停止去愛那個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:11.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  儘管我幫不了忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我其實也想跟你們共同進退
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絲莉亞為何…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不設計些男性用的裝甲服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但待我試試男扮女裝吧  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.62,0:08:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.73,0:08:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們很相配呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:45.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里昂仔一定是怕老婆那類型的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.14,0:08:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有…兩小時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.71,0:09:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們何時起在那裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我們先來這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來你們眼中只有對方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.92,0:09:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們真囉嗦  那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:11.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有辦法追上格拉迪亞了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用「種子島」的火箭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:18.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,單靠我們不可能開動那種東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我找到一條…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.77,0:09:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定能先格拉迪亞一步…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.17,0:09:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去到目的地的路線
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:47.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絲莉亞  我們去追格拉迪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…絲莉亞  我感謝你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  我想做自己做得到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米奇拜託你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.44,0:10:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一定會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絲莉亞  米奇一定會記起你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有我…他也一定會記起的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很寧靜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.96,0:10:23.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待我告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我討厭AD警察的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前住在一所工場的遺址
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一日  失常亞人闖進來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後來  我們趕到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.21,0:10:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們當時失手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們收拾了牠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.68,0:10:44.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們連裝甲車也衝進來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:47.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不停開鎗  子彈多到堆積如山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.49,0:10:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…那…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:51.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當時  你受了傷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:10:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我非常寶貴的碟卻燒毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.83,0:11:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.23,0:11:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常喜歡的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我總有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.77,0:11:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會在一大班觀眾面前唱出那首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.94,0:11:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是那種原因嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:17.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Skyhook每一日…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都會來到運輸艇的月台一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.69,0:11:23.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那是專門用來運送貨櫃的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.92,0:11:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  我們要在運輸艇開動前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.09,0:11:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走進貨櫃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Skyhook…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會夾起我們藏身的貨櫃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝宇宙飛上去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:11:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唱你想唱的那首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.23,0:12:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是觀眾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,運輸艇已經開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距離Skyhook來到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,足足還有一個多小時…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.47,0:13:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布烈絲  怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.41,0:13:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.14,0:13:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它掉進海裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連接收艇也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:42.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡也因為費挪現象…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布烈絲  怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使沒有運輸艇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Skyhook也會準時來到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:50.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它來到也不會停下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當Skyhook經過月台時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時速會高達780公里的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你死心吧  我們沒其他辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:16.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.37,0:14:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們還在做什麼  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使這個地球變成亞人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.92,0:14:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也毫不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.22,0:14:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  一定要活著回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三個人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里昂仔不能說得好一點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他看來已經盡了力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.84,0:15:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們捉緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.27,0:15:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.34,0:15:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rock’n roll
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們很重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:49.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布烈絲  你指裝甲服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.13,0:15:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,0:16:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.39,0:16:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點…再快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.26,0:16:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Motoslave
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.70,0:16:33.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是亞人吧  顯示你的決心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了  有機會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.61,0:16:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們去宇宙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮娜  開動噴射器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮娜  蓮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.56,0:17:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…未死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我未死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Knight Sabers飛上宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還是去那邊的駕駛室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.37,0:17:49.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儘管能靠裝甲服進行內部合成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.14,0:17:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,氧氣也不會永遠用不完
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.18,0:17:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.59,0:18:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.59,0:18:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒得到批准的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.30,0:18:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不能乘坐這部太空梭的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.17,0:18:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我無禮  我要通知控制中心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個亞人沒失常嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該說…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.21,0:18:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牠不過仍是個為人類服務的亞人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞人的真面目是格拉迪亞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.65,0:18:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  亞人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.51,0:18:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是有買票的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  那我剛才失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.49,0:18:39.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  請你們慢慢享受宇宙之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.46,0:18:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不會給你騙到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亞人  控制中心裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒有回應你的亞人或人類吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.97,0:18:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  已經有一星期失去聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.54,0:18:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那使我無法執行上頭的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.71,0:19:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  我向你發出新的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.28,0:19:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  什麼命令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星星有古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.69,0:19:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它們不閃的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.72,0:19:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有空氣  那是當然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你來到宇宙卻毫不感動的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.16,0:19:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.86,0:19:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.93,0:19:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小時候  我的夢想是當太空人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  那為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉你只要肯努力…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.74,0:19:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不夠高
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不甘心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當宇宙開發公團的人來通知我時
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.85,0:19:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吧  你實現夢想了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.55,0:19:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  蓮娜你亦一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.46,0:19:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然加入Knight Sabers是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.56,0:19:50.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我沒想過我甚至會來宇宙的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布烈絲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.44,0:20:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做得很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.98,0:20:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是那樣子  你也是亞人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.45,0:20:12.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  我起初不願意駕駛你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.49,0:20:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這件裝甲服亦一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.95,0:20:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  只要心靈相通
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.46,0:20:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞人也不會全部變成…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格拉迪亞般的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.89,0:20:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞人能變成我們人類的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.64,0:20:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種想法太單方面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太一廂情願
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.48,0:20:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.16,0:20:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有四小時
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.17,0:21:00.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才去到傘子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.23,0:21:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格拉迪亞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.67,0:21:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你忍耐一會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.04,0:21:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好積蒙塔沒有裝上火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.68,0:21:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要感謝積蒙的會長先生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.68,0:21:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能比格拉迪亞先一步去到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不能  那便後果堪虞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.62,0:21:25.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…請問格拉迪亞是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.86,0:21:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是新的亞人管理員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.17,0:21:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  她想以神的身分管理地球
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.31,0:22:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繁星點點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:24.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美麗  有這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.41,0:23:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我們終於去到…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.64,0:24:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,素成計劃的中樞「傘子系統」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.25,0:24:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那裡已經變成格拉迪亞的魔城
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.65,0:24:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像病灶一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.72,0:24:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞人的蛋不停繁殖
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.75,0:24:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟著輪到我們的白色影子出現
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.89,0:24:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格拉迪亞究竟有何計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.89,0:24:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回  吹波糖危機

